Jetpackimatica
by ApothecaryOfLight

A simple Jetpack mod.


REQUIREMENTS
-Default
-3darmor
-modlib


OPTIONAL DEPENDENCIES
-Technic
-Mesecon
-Hudbar


EXISTING FEATURES:
-Basic Jetpack (placeholder model)
-Super Jetpack (placeholder model)
-Flight
-No fall damage (temporary, will be configurable or highest tier)


ROADMAP:
-Add modlib log support.
-Place required and optional dependencies in mod.conf.
-Config file allowing you to set speeds, energy expenditure rate, fall damage.
-Jetpack models and textures
-6 tiers of jetpacks
-Chargable jetpacks
-Optional compatability with Technic
-Optional compatability with Mesecon
-Optional compatability with Hudbar
-Optional compatability with MoreMinerals
-Custom exhaust effects (lightning, green mist, rainbow, etc.)
